@startuml

title backend アーキテクチャ構造図

top to bottom direction
hide methods
skinparam classAttributeIconSize 0
skinparam packageStyle rectangle
skinparam nodesep 40
skinparam ranksep 80
skinparam ArrowFontSize 10

skinparam package {
    BackgroundColor #f7f9fc
    BorderColor #546e7a
    FontColor #243447
}
skinparam class {
    BackgroundColor #ffffff
    BorderColor #546e7a
    FontColor #243447
}

package "Backend Bootstrap" as BootstrapLayer {
    class "Backend Bootstrap" as BackendBootstrap {
        + production graph を手動 DI で組み立てる
        + concrete 実装を接続する
    }
}

package "Controller" as TransportLayer {
    class "Controller" as Controller {
        + Wails Bind の入口
        + request / response DTO を写像する
        + caller-owned UseCasePort を起動する
    }

    class "UseCasePort" as UseCasePort {
        + controller 依存境界
    }

    Controller -[hidden]down-> UseCasePort
}

package "Backend UseCase" as ApplicationLayer {
    class "Backend UseCase" as BackendUseCase {
        + query / command / import を orchestrate する
        + job 状態と完了 payload を扱う
    }

    class "ServicePort" as ServicePort {
        + usecase 依存境界
    }

    class "RuntimeEventPublisherPort" as RuntimeEventPublisherPort {
        + runtime event 完了 payload 境界
    }

    class "StateMachine" as StateMachine {
        + 状態遷移規則だけを持つ
    }

    class "JobIOService" as JobIOService {
        + job 状態を取得 / 保存する
    }

    BackendUseCase -[hidden]down-> ServicePort
    ServicePort -[hidden]right-> RuntimeEventPublisherPort
    RuntimeEventPublisherPort -[hidden]right-> StateMachine
    StateMachine -[hidden]right-> JobIOService
}

package "Service" as ServiceLayer {
    class "Service" as Service {
        + CRUD / import の実処理を担う
        + concrete API を直接持たない
    }

    class "RepositoryPort" as RepositoryPort {
        + 永続化境界
    }

    class "XMLFilePort" as XmlFilePort {
        + path 解決 / file open 境界
    }

    class "XMLRecordReaderPort" as XmlRecordReaderPort {
        + XML record 読み出し境界
    }

    class "RuntimeContextPort" as RuntimeContextPort {
        + progress event 境界
    }

    RepositoryPort -[hidden]right-> XmlFilePort
    XmlFilePort -[hidden]right-> XmlRecordReaderPort
    XmlRecordReaderPort -[hidden]right-> RuntimeContextPort
}

package "Adapter 群" as AdapterLayer {
    class "Repository" as RepositoryAdapter {
        + SQLite などの concrete 永続化
    }

    class "XML adapter: file" as XmlFileAdapter {
        + file path / open の concrete 実装
    }

    class "XML adapter: reader" as XmlReaderAdapter {
        + decoder の concrete 実装
    }

    class "Runtime adapter" as RuntimeAdapter {
        + Wails runtime へ event を送る
    }

    class "AIProvider" as AiProvider {
        + provider 差異を吸収する
    }

    RepositoryAdapter -[hidden]right-> XmlFileAdapter
    XmlFileAdapter -[hidden]right-> XmlReaderAdapter
    XmlReaderAdapter -[hidden]right-> RuntimeAdapter
    RuntimeAdapter -[hidden]right-> AiProvider
}

BackendBootstrap --> Controller : 手動 DI

Controller --> UseCasePort : 依存する
UseCasePort --> BackendUseCase : 実装する

BackendUseCase --> ServicePort : 依存する
ServicePort --> Service : 実装する
BackendUseCase --> StateMachine : 状態遷移を使う
BackendUseCase --> JobIOService : job 状態を扱う
BackendUseCase --> RuntimeEventPublisherPort : 完了 payload を扱う

Service --> RepositoryPort : 依存する
Service --> XmlFilePort : 依存する
Service --> XmlRecordReaderPort : 依存する
Service --> RuntimeContextPort : 依存する
Service --> AiProvider : 必要時に依存する

RepositoryPort --> RepositoryAdapter : 実装する
XmlFilePort --> XmlFileAdapter : 実装する
XmlRecordReaderPort --> XmlReaderAdapter : 実装する
RuntimeContextPort --> RuntimeAdapter : 実装する
RuntimeEventPublisherPort --> RuntimeAdapter : 実装する

BootstrapLayer -[hidden]down-> TransportLayer
TransportLayer -[hidden]down-> ApplicationLayer
ApplicationLayer -[hidden]down-> ServiceLayer
ServiceLayer -[hidden]down-> AdapterLayer

BackendBootstrap -[hidden]down-> Controller
Controller -[hidden]down-> BackendUseCase
BackendUseCase -[hidden]down-> Service
Service -[hidden]down-> RepositoryAdapter

legend bottom
    architecture.md の構造主語と節名に合わせる。
    層をまたぐ主依存は上から下に読む。
    Bootstrap の concrete 生成線は見やすさのため要約する。
endlegend

@enduml
